ReproLevel licensing
====================

Unless stated otherwise, this repository uses a dual-licensing approach:

1. Written content and documentation are licensed under the
   Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY 4.0).
2. Code, configuration, templates, and automation files are licensed
   under the MIT License.

This split is intended to reflect the mixed nature of the repository:
framework prose and level descriptions on the one hand, and reusable
repository infrastructure on the other.

Content license
---------------

The following are licensed under CC BY 4.0 unless a file says otherwise:

- Markdown prose and narrative framework content
- figures and documentation text
- manuscript text and related explanatory materials

